      • orderEntities

        public void orderEntities(String orderKeys)
        Sorts the entities according to the value of orderKeys. orderKeys = String of paired 'words', consisting of "AttributeName x", where x is A for ascending, or D for descending. i.e., "LastName A FirstName A". A context may be specified for the sorting attribute by putting the context name in square brackets ("[" and "]" after the sort order: "LastName A State A [Abbrev]"
